&lt;p&gt;We are looking for an organized, detail-driven Launch Coordinator who thrives at the intersection of project coordination and mobile marketing execution. Our ideal candidate is eager to own the end-to-end onboarding and launch experience for new customers, working cross-functionally to ensure every campaign goes live on time, on brand, and with precision. An ideal candidate brings strong project management instincts, a growth mindset, empathy for customers and colleagues, and a passion for helping enterprise brands make a powerful first impression on the Vibes platform.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role is central to Vibes ability to deliver a world-class onboarding experience. You will manage simultaneous customer launches, coordinate across internal teams and external stakeholders, and execute the hands-on platform work that brings new programs to life. Success in this role requires equal parts project management rigor and executional excellence.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a full-time, hybrid position in Chicago, IL reporting to the Director of Launch Services. Vibes has been recognized in 2025 as a Built In Best Hybrid Places to Work.&lt;/p&gt;
