&lt;h4&gt;&lt;em&gt;Project Management &amp;amp; Launch Coordination&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Project management of new customer launches, including scoping timelines, tracking milestones, coordinating deliverables, and communicating status to internal and external stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain and update launch project plans, ensuring all tasks are assigned, dependencies are identified, and deadlines are met.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as primary point of contact for customers during onboarding.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate launch activities internally to ensure all inputs needed for a successful launch are delivered on schedule.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Facilitate kickoff calls and regular check-ins with brand marketers and internal account teams, keeping all parties aligned and accountable.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify and escalate blockers quickly; problem-solve to keep launches on track.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
