&lt;li&gt;Deliver strong internal and external communication; keep stakeholders in the loop&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage short-code inventory and process weekly reports&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrate strong attention to detail in all interactions with partner companies; maintain “good standing partner” relationship&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Learn and understand industry and government compliance practices related to mobile; develop internal documentation for Vibes employees; Keep key stakeholders (Customer Success, Sales, etc.) up-to-date with changes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage industry and carrier auditing processes, including tracking, reporting, communication with internal teams and industry partners&lt;/li&gt;
